_text = "However the sun was beginning to set. The heat from earlier was still present, but cooling down as the sun descended. Tonight was our last night before we had to return home.\n\nThat night I choose to sleep outside in the hammock rather than in my tent. I think even back then I knew how important this night would be.\n\nI watched the stars twirl in the night sky above me. It felt freeing sleeping with nothing protecting you from the outside world. I felt myself open up to the world around me, letting every worry fissel as I rocked with the wind. The The wind swayed me to sleep that night, as the world around me went silent for the first time.\n\nI awoke the next morning to get ready to leave.\n\nDo I stay (Left) or do I go (Right)"

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, Monitor, MonitorNo, MonitorYes, HammockMemory, EllasCarMemory, false)
